    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款 2D 可爱风格的抓娃娃模拟器。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个抓娃娃世界里，拥有 41 个可爱的娃娃。并且，每一个娃娃都配备了专属的娃娃机，让您能充分感受到专属的抓取乐趣。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/f22b32faec00955a87dd9aa2182c2d8e.poster.avif?t=1753985622\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/f22b32faec00955a87dd9aa2182c2d8e.webm?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/f22b32faec00955a87dd9aa2182c2d8e.mp4?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个娃娃都设置了 5 种品质等级。品质越高的娃娃，其抓取的概率也就越低。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/3f02862c387a70d711bdeeff88bd2e96.poster.avif?t=1753985622\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/3f02862c387a70d711bdeeff88bd2e96.webm?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/3f02862c387a70d711bdeeff88bd2e96.mp4?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在操控方面，我模拟了真实爪子的力度和速度变化，让您在操作时需要考虑角度和时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更有趣的是，游戏里还有可爱的妹妹帮您抱娃娃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/57520b45dd70b72503d6235bd6efbced.poster.avif?t=1753985622\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/57520b45dd70b72503d6235bd6efbced.webm?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/57520b45dd70b72503d6235bd6efbced.mp4?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，游戏内提供了展示柜。在这里，您可以展示自己辛辛苦苦抓到的娃娃，欣赏它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/b934c1cb99eee93afe5ed09d45bfad9c.poster.avif?t=1753985622\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/b934c1cb99eee93afe5ed09d45bfad9c.webm?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162260/extras/b934c1cb99eee93afe5ed09d45bfad9c.mp4?t=1753985622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
